    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="predegree-intro">
        <h1>Your Gateway to <span>Degree Admission</span></h1>
        <p>The Pre-Degree (JUPEB) programme is a one-year foundation course that prepares students for Direct Entry admission into 200-level across all faculties. It is equivalent to the A-Level GCE, IJMB, and the Old Higher School Certificate.</p>

        <div class="predegree-stats">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h3>1 Year</h3>
                <p>Programme Duration</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h3>10</h3>
                <p>Faculties Available</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h3>200 Level</h3>
                <p>Direct Entry Access</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <h3>₦17,500</h3>
                <p>Application Fee</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info Banner -->
    <div class="predegree-banner">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
        <p>
            <strong>JUPEB Certification:</strong> Upon completion, students receive a Joint Universities Preliminary Examinations Board (JUPEB) Certificate which is accepted for Direct Entry admission at StanEdu and other JUPEB-affiliated universities in Nigeria and abroad. Candidates must also satisfy individual departmental admission requirements.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- How to Apply Steps -->
    <div class="how-to-apply">
        <h2>How to Apply</h2>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to secure your Pre-Degree admission</p>

        <div class="steps-row">
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h4>Buy EPin</h4>
                <p>Purchase your application EPin (₦17,500) online using your bank debit card</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h4>Fill Form</h4>
                <p>Complete the online application form using your EPin code</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h4>Submit Documents</h4>
                <p>Submit your O'Level result, birth certificate, and two reference letters</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <h4>Check Admission</h4>
                <p>Check your admission status on the portal using your form number</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">5</div>
                <h4>Pay School Fees</h4>
                <p>Accept your offer and pay school fees to complete clearance</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

